summary: This document appears to be a confidential report from AT&T regarding the location data of a mobile number associated with an investigation. It includes details about the confidence level of the location data and the data source used for tracking. The document emphasizes caution in using the location data for investigative purposes due to potential inaccuracies.
keyFacts: The document contains location data for a mobile number.
The data was initiated on July 1, 2020.
The confidence level of the location data is reported as 90.
The location data is sourced from AT&T's 4G-GMPC system.
